org.chronos.chronograph.api.structure

Interface ChronoVertex

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChronoElement, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.util.Host, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChronoVertexImpl, ChronoVertexProxy

    public interface ChronoVertex
extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex, ChronoElement
    The ChronoGraph-specific representation of the general-purpose TinkerPop Vertex interface.

    This interface defines additional methods for all graph elements, mostly intended for internal use only.
